author: thePunderWoman
message:
ci: update l2 triage label configuration for pull requests (#39954)

This updates the angular-robot.yml to remove two labels from
l2TriageLabels for PRs.

PR Close #39954

files.patch:
@@ -187,8 +187,6 @@ triagePR:

   l2TriageLabels:
     -
-      - "effort*"
-      - "risk*"
       - "comp: *"
